00:22:44,110 --> 00:22:46,290
to be close to 2.

377
00:22:46,290 --> 00:22:51,420
So since y is most likely to be
close to 0 or close to most

378
00:22:51,420 --> 00:22:53,850
of the probability
of y is here.

