451
00:26:56,190 --> 00:26:59,710
This procedure, what this
formula does is --

452
00:26:59,710 --> 00:27:04,490
nicely illustrated sort
of by mechanically.

453
00:27:04,490 --> 00:27:08,640
So let me show you a picture
